data.description: Santa may not be real but miracles do exist. How about this deal ?? Are you looking for a three bedroom two bath home listed for less than $200,000 on Acreage? They simply don’t exist in Garland County…… until now!!!  This is an absolute steal of the deal. Yes, Home needs some TLC and some repairs done but it would be well worth your money time and effort. Seller has said he would be willing to allow a repair allowance closing.    This beautiful little home is perfectly nestled in the woods on 15 acres m/l +-  just passed Lake Hamilton School District. Prime land for hunting surrounded by trees and wildlife and the land has tons of possibilities. This is a 1996 stick build (not a MH). Fantastic floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. No carpet! Get the bonfire ready for those cozy country nights.. conventional or cash only
